Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest export

Purpose:
  Export a projection from the archive.

Usage:
  spinedigest export <archive.sdpub> --output-format <format> [--output <path>]

Contract:
  - Mutates: no.
  - LLM: no.
  - JSON: no.
  - Formats: markdown, txt, epub, sdpub.

Examples:
  spinedigest export book.sdpub --output-format markdown --output digest.md
